name: BusinessNameUSA
overview:
BusinessNameUSA.com makes it easy and accessible for businesses to obtain business legal documents online.

Using BusinessNameUSA.com Legal Document Service can reduce the time required to obtain business licenses, tax ids and company formation services. It also provides live, free legal advice by a licensed lawyer. The information helps visitors make an informed decision about what legal documents are required to operate a business and then obtain them right there and then at a very affordable price.

BusinessNameUSA.com also makes it easy to immediately chat with a lawyer when necessary, completely online from one’s home or computer.

BusinessNameUSA.com provides a licensed attorney to inform visitors about what documents are legally required to start a business. The filings of business licenses, tax ids and company formations are quick, inexpensive and legally conforming.
